<sect2>
<title>Installation de libxslt</title>

<para>Installez libxslt en lançant les commandes suivantes:</para>

<para><screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</userinput></screen></para>

